CM_ BO_ 596 "Wheel speed broadcast. 4 x uint15 wheel speeds in gradians/second (400 gradians = 1 wheel revolution). Field order is RL, RR, FL, FR (rear axle precedes front). Bit 15 of each 16-bit field is a 'valid' flag (1 = valid). Invalid pattern: lower 15 bits all set (0x7FFF). wheel_rpm = raw * 60 / 400 = raw * 0.15. Final-drive ratio = tailshaft_rpm / wheel_rpm. The RL/RR-first ordering was confirmed by the F20 dyno capture, where only the driven (rear) wheels remain valid while the lifted front wheels are flagged invalid.";

